query:
SELECT
                id,
                created_at AS "created_at: DateTime<Utc>",
                data       AS "data: SerializedJournalistToUserDeadDropMessages",
                signature  AS "signature: Signature<JournalistToUserDeadDropSignatureDataV2>"
            FROM user_dead_drops
            WHERE id > $1
            ORDER BY id ASC
            LIMIT $2
